## Refutation / known limits
- The docs are SNAPSHOTS. The MCP spec evolves; skills-hub may
  change behaviour; future MCP servers may diverge differently.
  The four documented divergences (D01-D04) should be re-verified
  before any 0.7.0 implementation lands.
- UX-FINDINGS-0.6.0.md is single-session, single-model
  (llama3.2:latest). Different models will have different failure
  modes. The 80% native-tool-call rate is specific to llama3.2 on
  this hardware, NOT a general claim about sage.
- Neither document is a contract — they're observation reports.

